{"id":277047,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-50余名维权者中纪委门前举行抗议活动（图/","date":"2013-01-30T15:16:10Z","modified":"2013-01-30T15:16:10Z","title":"维权网 |  50余名维权者中纪委门前举行抗议活动（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员杭审报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span>1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>时</span><span>许，来自北京、天津、河北、河南、黑龙江、辽宁、江苏、陕西等地，还有几名蒙冤警察在内的，近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>余名维权者不约而同的到中纪委门前举行抗议活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>尽管大家来自不同的地区，案件也各自不同，但是一个共同点目标——反腐维权！大家要反应的问题只有一个，中纪委和各地纪委部门监管不利，严重失职而培养出这无数贪官，导致出举国上下诸多冤假错案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>抗议者说：今天我们的国家腐败已经无孔不入，坑民、害民、勒索民财、社会到了民不聊生的地步。小：幼儿园的校车，带走了那么多的小生命；大：国有资产流失，省部级、直至中央领导贪污腐败，若干个亿的钱财中饱私囊。而百姓只能勒紧裤腰带过紧日子……国家兴亡，匹夫有责。今天众匹夫前来中纪委抗议，是尽我们的微薄之力挽救我们国家。同时也告知天下人：不治理腐败，亡党大势所趋，亡国不能容忍！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Zi5W0H_iAr0/UQk1lKomZfI/AAAAAAAAazQ/UOOrHox_N4U/s1600/P290113_0906.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Zi5W0H_iAr0/UQk1lKomZfI/AAAAAAAAazQ/UOOrHox_N4U/s400/P290113_0906.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-y4X5xOqZLK0/UQk1rQsJQUI/AAAAAAAAazg/sm7voovwbOw/s1600/%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-y4X5xOqZLK0/UQk1rQsJQUI/AAAAAAAAazg/sm7voovwbOw/s400/%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D6.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-g2NwDf4Pqec/UQk2GgeBomI/AAAAAAAAazw/_HpLARv3cek/s1600/P290113_1449.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"h